contents.author: Soju | X
contents.content:
Channel: #announcements

**@everyone

The vote to fund the very first Jupiter working group is live!

This vote will be crucial in setting the precedent for working groups to come, to help drive forward the vision of the Jupiverse. Over the last week the Core Working Group has spent time engaged in community discussions and had a robust back and forth with the community to finalize their budget proposal.

Cast your vote here: https://vote.jup.ag/proposal/5N9UbMGzga3SL8Rq7qDZCGfZX3FRDUhgqkSY2ksQjg8r

Go out there and make your voice heard!

Outline of Proposal Details: https://www.jupresear.ch/t/proposal-core-working-group-budget/12689
CWG Clip at the Planetary Call: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4lUAszogT5c 
Meow interviews the CWG: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=boBGcPAKci0

As a reminder, participating in votes gives you rewards, no matter the outcome or the option you choose.
Go out there and vote, catdets! Make your voice heard! **

contents.author: Herotime
contents.content:
Channel: #announcements

Look back to look forward.

In the past 6 years GAIMIN has:
🎮  Built a top 5 global Esports organization, which in 2023 achieved 10b impressions, 5 tier-1 major wins and 53 top 3 placings.

🖥️  Built a gaming platform that is the worlds largest source of decentralized GPUs (while in beta)

:tm8badgeyellow:  Become CoinMarketCap's first ever incubated project

:btc:  Been named the Web3 Gaming Ambassadors of BNB Chain

💪  Built partnerships with the world's largest supply side aggregators for GPUs

----------

Sometimes a reminder is nice to know where we have been to see the trajectory of where we are going.

GAIMIN is a multi million dollar business and this marks day 5 after a successful TGE, deemed top 2 out of Bybit's last 3 months.

We achieved 33M post impressions of the GAIMIN account in 15 days and achieved the most hyped project status for 12 days leading into TGE. Now everyone knows who we are...so they're about to see what comes next 😉 

GAIMIN has been building for the past 6 years and one thing we know for sure, GAIMIN will be around for another 6 years and beyond @everyone

contents.author: Gaimin
contents.content:
For those asking about initial circulating supply - 5% LP is locked permanently 👇

For CoinMarketCap ranking purposes of circulating supply and market cap, you will see a 6.5% initial circulating supply.  

It is 1.5% initial circulating supply, as detailed in previous posts, plus 5% Liquidity (LP), as shown in our tokenomics, totaling 6.5%.  

The LP is locked permanently for liquidity on exchanges, however for tracking and ranking purposes you will see 6.5% on CoinMarketCap âœ…

You will see this gradually increase over time as unlock schedules happen through vesting.
